name: Detalle Ordenes y Materiales Liquidados
query:
select sle.posting_date, sle.posting_time,warehouse, sle.item_code, sle.stock_uom, sle.actual_qty, sle.qty_after_transaction, sle.voucher_no, 
  case when sle.actual_qty < 0 then "Salida" else  "Entrada" end as tipo_movimiento,
  case when (select stock_entry_type from `tabStock Entry` se where se.name = sle.voucher_no) = "Material Issue" then  
  (select service_order from vw_expediciones_crm where vw_expediciones_crm.name = sle.voucher_no limit 1 ) 
  else (select stock_entry_type from `tabStock Entry` se where se.name = voucher_no) end as orden_de_servicio 
  from `tabStock Ledger Entry` sle inner join  `tabAlmacenes de Tecnico` atec on sle.warehouse = atec.almacen
  where sle.is_cancelled = 0 and atec.parent = (SELECT t.name from `tabTecnico` t where t.usuario_reporte = %(user)s)
 ORDER BY sle.posting_date asc, sle.posting_time asc
